  "title": "Aerospace/ Aircraft Technician x5 (MRO/ Engine & Parts) - East, MNC [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Exciting Career Opportunities – Multiple Roles Available! 🚀</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Salary: $2,300 - $3,000 + Allowances + OT</li>\n  <li>Attractive Bonuses &amp; Career Growth</li>\n  <li>Shift Allowance (for shift-based roles)</li>\n  <li>5-Day Work Week | Office Hours</li>\n  <li>Location: East</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform maintenance, repair, and overhaul (MRO) of aircraft components and systems.</li>\n  <li>Inspect, troubleshoot, and replace faulty parts in engines, avionics, and airframe structures.</li>\n  <li>Conduct routine servicing and ensure compliance with safety and aviation standards.</li>\n  <li>Use specialized tools and equipment to test and certify aircraft components.</li>\n  <li>Follow technical manuals and work closely with engineers to maintain quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Document maintenance work and update service records.</li>\n  <li>Ensure workplace safety and adhere to regulatory guidelines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Entry Level are welcome to apply. Training will be provided</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Candidate with experiences either in Engine/ Assembly/ Component/ Mechanical will also have added advantages</strong></li>\n  <li>Nitec/ Higher Nitec/ Diploma in Aeronautical/ Aerospace/ Mechanical / Mechatronics or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Experience in aviation/ aerospace industry will have added advantages but not compulsory</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"<strong>APPLY NOW</strong>\" button</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</strong></p>",
